name: DBL - Habano - El Rey XV
additionalNotes: It is my honor to recognize their Dad’s successful career in the cigar industry with the introduction of our first series, The Habano line is a special edition that pays homage to their Dad’s cigar brand from the 1980s.The Habano is a rich and complex cigar that packs more flavor than strength and encompasses plenty of rich family history. The final blend is the end result of a painstaking process in which countless blends were tested, retested and tested again by a tasting panel comprised of several cigar aficionados. DBL Habano features a stunning Ecuador Habano wrapper, a Dominican binder and a filler blend of Dominican and Nicaraguan tobacco.
